[INSTRUCTIONS]
Using ONLY the search results above as your source for federal programs and comparable cities:
- Federal programs must appear in the search results above — do not invent programs.
- Comparable cities: extract ANY city mentioned in the global search results (even as an example or case study). If the article mentions Chicago, St. Louis, Rochester — include them. Do not invent cities not mentioned in the results.
- Montgomery recommendations must be grounded in the real statistics from DATA.
- If a field is unavailable from the search results, use null. Do not leave comparable_cities empty if any city is mentioned in the results.

